mm/huge_memory.c: split_huge_pages_fops should be defined with DEFINE_DEBUGFS_ATTRIBUTE

split_huge_pages_fops is used for debugfs file.  hence, it is more clear
to use DEFINE_DEBUGFS_ATTRIBUTE.

